# 3. Keywords for Modifiers (11)

These modify classes, methods, and variables.

| Keyword      | Purpose                     | Example                       |
| ------------ | --------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| public       | Accessible everywhere       | `public class Test`           |
| private      | Accessible within class     | `private int id;`             |
| protected    | Package + subclass          | `protected void show()`       |
| static       | Belongs to class            | `static int count;`           |
| final        | Cannot change               | `final int MAX = 100;`        |
| abstract     | Incomplete class/method     | `abstract class Shape`        |
| synchronized | Thread safety               | `synchronized void deposit()` |
| native       | Calls native code           | `native void print();`        |
| strictfp     | Floating-point precision    | `strictfp class Demo`         |
| transient    | Ignore during serialization | `transient String password;`  |
| volatile     | Updated across threads      | `volatile boolean running;`   |

### Example

```java
public class Employee {

    public static String company = "TCS";

    private int id;

    final double PI = 3.14;
}
```

