# 5. Class Related Keywords (6)

| Keyword    | Purpose                  | Example                        |
| ---------- | ------------------------ | ------------------------------ |
| class      | Create class             | `class Employee`               |
| package    | Organize classes         | `package com.bank;`            |
| import     | Import package           | `import java.util.*;`          |
| extends    | Inheritance              | `class Dog extends Animal`     |
| implements | Interface implementation | `class Car implements Vehicle` |
| interface  | Create interface         | `interface Payment`            |

### Example

```java
package com.bank;

interface Payment {

    void pay();
}

class UPI implements Payment {

    public void pay() {
        System.out.println("UPI Payment");
    }
}
```

