# 6. Object Related Keywords (4)

| Keyword    | Purpose             | Example                   |
| ---------- | ------------------- | ------------------------- |
| new        | Create object       | `new Employee();`         |
| instanceof | Check object type   | `obj instanceof Employee` |
| super      | Access parent class | `super.display();`        |
| this       | Current object      | `this.id = id;`           |

### Example

```java
class Animal {

    void sound() {
        System.out.println("Animal");
    }
}

class Dog extends Animal {

    Dog() {
        super.sound();
    }
}

public class Test {

    int id;

    Test(int id) {
        this.id = id;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        Dog d = new Dog();

        System.out.println(d instanceof Dog);
    }
}
```

Output:

```text
Animal
true
```

